Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.25,0:01:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就再見了 凱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.05,0:01:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.95,0:01:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自來也大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您一定要找到綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.55,0:01:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.95,0:01:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定會找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.55,0:01:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且會立刻帶她回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.15,0:02:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡像你這樣有幹勁的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.95,0:02:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就送給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李就是靠這個變強的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.35,0:02:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼 是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.25,0:02:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透氣性 保溫性都非常優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.65,0:02:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還有易於行動的\N完美外形以及美麗線條
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.45,0:02:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修煉的時候穿上的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.45,0:02:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就會感到有所不同
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你立刻就會愛上它的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.05,0:02:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也會像小李一樣 一直穿在身上的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.15,0:02:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 我也很喜歡這件衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.65,0:03:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其隨身帶這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.79,0:03:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不如帶面鏡子呢 傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿著會合身嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.45,0:03:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是看看你眼前的那個人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.15,0:03:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在難看死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是全鎮都是賭場的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.85,0:04:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的目標果然是鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.75,0:04:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把鳴人帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的組織曉 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所下達給我們的至上命令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.75,0:04:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好色仙人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的目標為什麼是我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好色仙人知道原因的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說他們的目標是你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不如說是你身體裡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙到底是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是襲擊木葉的怪物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.15,0:04:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家才會害怕它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼他們想得到它呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九尾的確自古以來就會出現在各個時代
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個會破壞一切的妖魔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以以前的人都會把它當成天災
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.75,0:05:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常害怕它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們為什麼想要這樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話我也猜不透他們的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是既然九尾封印在你的體內
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.55,0:05:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們應該就會想去控制那種力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然一直被追蹤對你而言很殘酷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這就是你的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 有我保護你 你就放心…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我必須趕快變強了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:05:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們趕快去找那個綱手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.55,0:06:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等她救完佐助 我們就趕快修煉去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.35,0:06:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像他的作風啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修煉開始 我絕對會變強
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.70,0:06:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.85,0:06:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不就是賭金最高的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好怕的 我們進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.55,0:06:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.65,0:06:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想採訪的那個美女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道就是綱手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.35,0:06:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真聰明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.65,0:06:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和好色仙人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是三忍之一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:06:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 那又怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人多大了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.45,0:07:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是老太婆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些錢 全部幫我換成籌碼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹勁十足的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.75,0:07:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位大姐到底是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙就是擁有那個綽號的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綽號
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.15,0:08:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 綱手是個怎麼樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 是一個討厭的傢伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且非常愛賭博
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界的人都知道她的長相
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定很快就能找到她了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個名人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她確實很有名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.95,0:08:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是那個傳說中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.45,0:08:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大 她的綽號到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傳說中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的…肥羊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然她是非常有名的肥羊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但應該沒那麼容易找到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她很討厭自己年老的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在應該用特殊的忍術改變了外貌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然實際上已經五十了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可看上去還是二十歲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近我還聽說她會隨機應變地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成十幾歲 三十幾歲 四十幾歲的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以此逃避上門來討債的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.85,0:09:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 真是亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.27,0:09:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手從小就喜歡賭博
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.95,0:09:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可她的運氣和實力卻差到了極點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.55,0:09:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她老是被贏錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才有那樣的綽號
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.85,0:09:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且她每次借完錢之後就逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讓人懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是懷念的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們該怎麼找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.55,0:10:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊 儘管只能一步步來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過方法還是很多的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那得花多長時間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會浪費時間的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,途中所有的時間我都會用在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用在我身上…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要用這段時間變強
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是修煉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.85,0:10:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.05,0:10:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就不用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.55,0:10:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想和穿著這種衣服的人走在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:10:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好色仙人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快開始修煉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要著急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要一邊收集綱手的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊修煉才有意義啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集情報
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個鎮子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.20,0:11:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是第一次來這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娛樂也是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們先好好休息一下再開始修煉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場慶典會持續一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間 我們就住在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修煉也在這裡進行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很有錢嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.10,0:12:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是財政部長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很有錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都是每次任務後一點點攢下的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.50,0:12:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的錢包由我來保管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.14,0:12:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能用的就只有這些啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有三百兩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要抱怨 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道忍者有三禁的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者的三禁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 你居然不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.30,0:12:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的忍者三禁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是指會危害忍者的三種慾望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是酒 女人和金錢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這跟我沒什麼關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒到二十歲 不能喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不懂什麼是對女人的慾望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這些錢都是我拚命存下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒打算把它都花完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看對金錢的慾望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一開始花錢 就停不下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.20,0:13:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金錢的魔力是很可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在要找的綱手就是被錢害了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好色仙人還不是\N一見到女人就欲罷不能了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.30,0:13:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在要開始收集情報了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.20,0:13:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你替我拿行李吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果迷路的話 就召喚追蹤用的蛤蟆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它會順著我的氣味 帶你找到我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是個孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.10,0:13:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 先去填飽肚子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 給我一個烤章魚丸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶油馬鈴薯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力香蕉也想要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:13:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏仁糖也好想要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.70,0:13:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,串燒也想要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:14:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 不要客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 來份炒麵 大份的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.48,0:14:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你買了不少吃的啊 孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會是一個人吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是一個人吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.10,0:14:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像吃得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都怎麼樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.10,0:14:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每天都要好好修煉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要變強以後再回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.80,0:14:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.50,0:14:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去消化消化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.60,0:14:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 全中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.90,0:14:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是手裡劍的修煉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子 你還真是執著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 你看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者們 這裡嚴禁使用忍術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.20,0:15:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴著面具在街上走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是很危險的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好色仙人的存折嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,個 十 百…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多零啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.40,0:15:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這麼多零平時都不肯請客
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:16:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下一點點了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逛完下一家就沒錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.20,0:16:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要用這段時間變強
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是修煉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 給我兩支烏賊燒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一支是給大人吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.78,0:16:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子 自己買東西 很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.70,0:16:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一支小孩吃的就送你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是老闆啊 太帥了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是慧眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.70,0:16:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 大人這支就收你半價吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.10,0:16:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 他到底跑哪兒去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是好色仙人的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年輕的女孩子真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 你逛完慶典了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者的三禁是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是說說看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然一下子就把三禁全破了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差勁的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你個頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把我拚命攢的錢都花完了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以後會還給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把我的青蛙給…可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.30,0:17:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混賬 你們在搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把我大哥的名牌衣服弄髒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快賠錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我拿十萬兩出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種衣服要十萬兩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種難看的衣服竟然讓他賠十萬兩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們有點過分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想打架嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們最好老實點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥以前可是巖隱的中忍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.60,0:17:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為傳說中的黑暗忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.90,0:18:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常厲害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.80,0:18:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你真想吃點苦頭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就讓你看看我要教你的忍術吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可要看仔細了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我怎麼收拾你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經盡量手下留情了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們實在是太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.30,0:18:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是那個傳說中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 把這裡弄成了這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.08,0:18:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就當作修理費吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:19:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想順便買下這裡所有的水球和氣球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.23,0:19:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.40,0:19:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是一般的掌擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.80,0:19:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的忍術究竟是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來吧 要去修煉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.10,0:19:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於要開始修煉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.20,0:19:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你 這個水球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.10,0:19:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個用來幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才有沒有仔細看我的那個忍術
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得那是什麼忍術
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像敵人被旋轉得很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然看錯了要點 可也大差不差了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就是旋轉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手沒動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.91,0:19:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水球裡的水卻旋轉了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.70,0:20:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在爬樹的修煉中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把查克拉維持在必要的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.70,0:20:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在水面行走的修煉中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須持續放出一定量的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩件事之前都已經練習過了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.20,0:20:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的水球修煉中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要製造查克拉的流動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是旋轉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製造查克拉的流動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳細的說明等你學會第一步再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.40,0:20:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先根據爬樹修煉的要領
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集查克拉並維持在手上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再按照水面行走的要領
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持續放出查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就是讓這個水球裡的水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在查克拉的作用下移動起來的一種修煉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要練到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水球裡旋轉的水能將水球弄破為止是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的變聰明了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.30,0:20:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 今天就練到晚上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.73,0:22:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.79,0:22:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要把這個水球弄破
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.94,0:22:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這股氣勢很可靠嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.71,0:22:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.82,0:22:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水旋轉起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.07,0:22:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水球到底什麼時候才會破呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.16,0:22:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.00,0:22:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毅力 水球破吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.61,0:23:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 為什麼不破啊
